{"thag6.5:0.1":"Theragatha 6.5 ","thag6.5:0.2":"Chakkanipata ","thag6.5:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag6.5:0.4":"Malukyaputtattheragatha ","thag6.5:1.1":"“Manujassa pamattacarino, ","thag6.5:1.2":"Tanha vaddhati maluva viya; ","thag6.5:1.3":"So plavati hura huram, ","thag6.5:1.4":"Phalamicchamva vanasmi vanaro. ","thag6.5:2.1":"Yam esa sahate jammi, ","thag6.5:2.2":"tanha loke visattika; ","thag6.5:2.3":"Soka tassa pavaddhanti, ","thag6.5:2.4":"abhivatthamva biranam. ","thag6.5:3.1":"Yo cetam sahate jammim, ","thag6.5:3.2":"tanham loke duraccayam; ","thag6.5:3.3":"Soka tamha papatanti, ","thag6.5:3.4":"udabinduva pokkhara. ","thag6.5:4.1":"Tam vo vadami bhaddam vo, ","thag6.5:4.2":"yavantettha samagata; ","thag6.5:4.3":"Tanhaya mulam khanatha, ","thag6.5:4.4":"usiratthova biranam; ","thag6.5:4.5":"Ma vo nalamva sotova, ","thag6.5:4.6":"maro bhanji punappunam. ","thag6.5:5.1":"Karotha buddhavacanam, ","thag6.5:5.2":"khano vo ma upaccaga; ","thag6.5:5.3":"Khanatita hi socanti, ","thag6.5:5.4":"nirayamhi samappita. ","thag6.5:6.1":"Pamado rajo pamado, ","thag6.5:6.2":"pamadanupatito rajo; ","thag6.5:6.3":"Appamadena vijjaya, ","thag6.5:6.4":"abbahe sallamattano”ti. ","thag6.5:6.5":"… Malukyaputto thero …. "}